Speaker 2: Yeah, I'd like to refill my prescription. I need your name and zip code.

Speaker 1: Michael Carvella, one six one zero one. Thank you.

Speaker 2: 401 Pearson Street.

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: You want to do the same amount of pills, 54 of them?

Speaker 1: Yep, and then am I using the same MasterCard, nine three seven four?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Hey Michael, we're all set. Your order went through successfully.

Speaker 2: I'm gonna get your prescription renewed just because it did expire. But once that happens, we'll mail this out. So you're all set.

Speaker 1: All right. Thank you. Thank you.
